    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><br>一款关于无人机寻找道路的物理平台游戏。你通过电光束悬浮在地面上。你的目标是调整推进器的角度，克服越来越难的障碍。操作虽然困难，但掌握后会非常有成就感！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252730/extras/1f4412c41becdcf30767bf0a2688de4d.poster.avif?t=1729703616\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252730/extras/1f4412c41becdcf30767bf0a2688de4d.webm?t=1729703616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252730/extras/1f4412c41becdcf30767bf0a2688de4d.mp4?t=1729703616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>如果你稍微用力撞到障碍物，你将从最后一个检查点重新开始。这可能会令人沮丧，但你可以暂停游戏，放松一下，聆听这段美妙的音乐。当你冷静下来后，再试一次——一次又一次地挑战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252730/extras/aae6773edcebea174fe1563affedbc14.poster.avif?t=1729703616\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252730/extras/aae6773edcebea174fe1563affedbc14.webm?t=1729703616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252730/extras/aae6773edcebea174fe1563affedbc14.mp4?t=1729703616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >控制</h2></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你使用鼠标在右侧的面板上控制无人机。当红点靠近面板的右侧时，右侧的推进器会启动，以此类推。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252730/extras/d51e1941427c89b5c3e317c9c15ae10c.poster.avif?t=1729703616\" width=720 height=576 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252730/extras/d51e1941427c89b5c3e317c9c15ae10c.webm?t=1729703616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252730/extras/d51e1941427c89b5c3e317c9c15ae10c.mp4?t=1729703616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你将红点放在面板的中间，无人机会平稳地悬浮在原地。就是这样。希望你能享受这段小小的冒险 ;)</p>",
